699
00:50:41,648 --> 00:50:43,475
And that's all there is to it.

700
00:50:44,609 --> 00:50:46,768
Is that all there is to it?

701
00:50:46,862 --> 00:50:49,354
Yeah. It's all there is to it.

702
00:50:58,125 --> 00:50:59,240
Peww!

703
00:51:02,255 --> 00:51:04,379
I'm not such a bad guy, you know.

704
00:51:06,093 --> 00:51:08,335
<i>Some folks have grown pretty fat off me.</i>

705
00:51:11,099 --> 00:51:13,139
Some have grown pretty dead.

706
00:51:17,732 --> 00:51:19,191
You're a conundrum, you.

707
00:51:21,528 --> 00:51:26,155
You walk in here shooting your fucking mouth off
like you don't give a fuck if it gets shot off.

708
00:51:27,452 --> 00:51:28,863
You can only kill me once.

709
00:51:36,879 --> 00:51:37,662
Checkmate.

710
00:51:44,180 --> 00:51:46,220
Nobody says I have to kill you quick.

711
00:51:49,603 --> 00:51:51,430
Cat.

712
00:51:52,523 --> 00:51:54,350
Mouse.

713
00:51:56,027 --> 00:51:58,067
You've got three days.

714
00:52:02,034 --> 00:52:04,074
Excuse me.

715
00:52:24,894 --> 00:52:26,519
Who the fuck is this guy?

716
00:52:27,523 --> 00:52:30,975
<i>Dunno. But whoever he is, he's either in</i>
